flowchart TD
    Login(["`**User logs in**
    POST /api/practitioners/auth/login/`"])

    TM["`**TenantMiddleware**
    Reads session → looks up Practitioner
    Attaches *request.tenant* from user FK`"]

    Request["`**API request arrives**
    DRF view receives request
    with *request.user* + *request.tenant*`"]

    SuperCheck{Is superuser?}

    SuperAllow(["`✓ **Allow — full access**
    Superuser bypasses all
    permission checks`"])

    LookupRoles["`**Look up user_roles**
    WHERE user_id = request.user.id`"]

    CollectPerms["`**Collect permissions**
    JOIN role_permissions ON role_id
    across all assigned roles
    → flat set of Module:Action keys`"]

    PermCheck{"`Has required
    *Module:Action*
    permission?`"}

    Allow(["`✓ **200 OK**
    View proceeds
    → Service → Repository → DB
    → serialised JSON response`"])

    Deny(["`✗ **403 Forbidden**
    JSON: detail: permission denied
    Frontend shows inline Alert
    No redirect`"])

    Login --> TM
    TM --> Request
    Request --> SuperCheck
    SuperCheck -->|Yes| SuperAllow
    SuperCheck -->|No| LookupRoles
    LookupRoles --> CollectPerms
    CollectPerms --> PermCheck
    PermCheck -->|Yes| Allow
    PermCheck -->|No| Deny

    style SuperAllow fill:#d1fae5,stroke:#10b981,color:#065f46
    style Allow      fill:#d1fae5,stroke:#10b981,color:#065f46
    style Deny       fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444,color:#991b1b
    style SuperCheck fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#78350f
    style PermCheck  fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b,color:#78350f
